    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "The 'Title' option is setup via the Global Sections for color swatches. The setup for the 'Image' is inferred from the first variant for the option. The 'Metafield' option is inferred from the first variant for the option and references the ProductVariant metafield: 'smart.color_swatch' which can be set to either 'color' or 'image'."
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_tooltip",
